FOR ME.

13:41.522 --> 13:43.991
[ MAXEEN MOANS]
GOOD NIGHT, ANDY.

13:44.024 --> 13:45.526
NIGHT, SHANE.

13:45.559 --> 13:46.860
Nancy: HI.

13:46.894 --> 13:49.062
YOU HAVE REACHED
THE OFFICE

13:49.096 --> 13:51.164
OF DOUGLAS WILSON

13:51.198 --> 13:56.637
AND HIS ASSISTANT, NANCY BOTWIN.

13:56.670 --> 13:58.038
IF YOU'VE REACHED THIS MESSAGE,

13:58.071 --> 14:01.041
I AM NO DOUBT SCRAMBLING
AROUND THE OFFICE,

14:01.074 --> 14:06.480
MOMENTS AWAY FROM ANSWERING
YOUR VERY IMPORTANT...

14:08.015 --> 14:12.219
...VERY IMPORTANT ‐‐
VERY...IMPORTANT...

14:13.120 --> 14:14.621
...IMPORTANT PHONE CALL.

14:14.655 --> 14:16.823
CODE RED, NANCE. 911.
INTO MY OFFICE, PRONTO.

14:16.857 --> 14:18.592
NO, I'M ‐‐ BUT ‐‐
NOW. NOW.

14:18.625 --> 14:19.860
NOW.

14:19.893 --> 14:20.928
OKAY.

14:20.961 --> 14:22.095
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

14:22.129 --> 14:25.999
HEY. HEY.
WHO'S THAT GUY?

14:26.033 --> 14:27.935
THE GUY IN THE SUIT?
NO IDEA.

14:27.968 --> 14:29.870
NO.
OH, WAIT. YEAH.
YEAH, YEAH. YEAH.

14:29.903 --> 14:32.139
YEAH, THAT'S ‐‐ THAT'S KLEIN,
THE C. E. O.

14:32.172 --> 14:35.008
I'M HAVING LUNCH WITH
JAPANESE COMPUTER EXECUTIVES.

14:35.042 --> 14:36.176
RED LIKE THE RISING SUN

14:36.210 --> 14:38.278
OR YELLOW
LIKE THEIR PAC‐MAN FACES?

14:38.312 --> 14:40.547
DOES YOUR, UH,
CELLPHONE HAVE A CAMERA?

14:40.581 --> 14:41.949
I THINK SO. BUT ‐‐
OKAY.

14:41.982 --> 14:43.483
I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.
NANCE.

14:46.220 --> 14:49.289
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATION ]

14:54.094 --> 14:55.929
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

14:55.963 --> 14:57.531
[ SHOUTING STOPS ]

15:01.835 --> 15:04.271
DENNY, NANCY.
NANCY, DENNY.

15:04.304 --> 15:05.873
HI.

15:05.906 --> 15:09.109
UH, I TAKE
THE LUNCH ORDERS.

15:09.142 --> 15:11.345
TELL HIM WHAT KIND OF WEED
YOU WANT. HE'LL GET IT.

15:13.447 --> 15:14.381
SHE'S COOL.

15:14.414 --> 15:17.818
I'LL TAKE 1/8 OF AK‐47,
1/8 OF WET JULIE.

15:17.851 --> 15:20.087
OUT OF JULIE.
I GOT GNARLY MARLY, KUSH.

15:20.120 --> 15:22.055
KUSH WORKS.
KUSH WORKS.

15:22.089 --> 15:23.190
NANCY? I'M BUYING.

15:23.223 --> 15:24.491
HE COMES BY TWICE A DAY,
10:00 AND 5:00.

15:24.525 --> 15:26.126
COVERS THE WHOLE BUILDING.

15:26.159 --> 15:29.162
OH, SHIT. IS THIS
MAKING YOU FEEL AWKWARD?

15:29.196 --> 15:31.164
SHE USED TO BE A ‐‐
NUN.

15:31.198 --> 15:33.200
SO, UM, IT'S OKAY.

15:33.233 --> 15:34.234
WICKED.

15:34.268 --> 15:37.638
BACK AT 5:00.
HAVE YOU BEEN WORKING OUT?

15:37.671 --> 15:39.306
OH, YOU NOTICED, HUH?

15:39.339 --> 15:40.607
NICE.

15:43.110 --> 15:45.445
YEAH, I THINK THE STEROIDS
ARE GIVING ME ACNE.

15:45.479 --> 15:47.147
HOLD THAT THOUGHT.
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS ]

15:47.181 --> 15:50.017
ON THE UP SIDE, I'VE LOST
ABOUT AN INCH ON MY DICK.

15:50.050 --> 15:51.418
SO NOW IT'S STRAIGHT.

15:51.451 --> 15:55.189
[ UP‐TEMPO DANCE MUSIC
PLAYING IN DISTANCE ]

15:55.222 --> 15:57.891
BEEN THERE, MAN.
IT HURTS.

15:57.925 --> 15:59.993
THEY SAID
MY FAT, CHUNKY FACE

16:00.027 --> 16:03.630
WOULD DISTRACT FROM
THEIR SLENDER FALL CAPRIS.

16:03.664 --> 16:04.965
WHAT'S WITH THAT?

16:04.998 --> 16:07.034
I DON'T KNOW.

16:07.067 --> 16:09.169
BUT...I OFFER THE CURE.

16:09.203 --> 16:12.172
AFGOOEY. PURE SATIVA.
BOTTLED AT THE SOURCE.

16:12.206 --> 16:13.674
